    "description": "BATCHIE is a Bayesian active learning platform for scalable combination drug screens that designs experiments dynamically in batches based on information theory and probabilistic modeling. It accurately predicts unseen combinations and detects synergies, enabling large-scale unbiased combination drug screens with a relatively small number of experiments.",
